Subject: SOP Job Node Browser Interface

Description: Canonical read-first interface contract for loading the SOP framework around a job node as an inspectable Codex app surface while sub-agent Codex CLI work stays gated underneath.

@ [source] C:\Project\Pinky\.sop\platform\source_documents\2026-06-25_sop_job_node_browser_interface\Dictated_SOP_Job_Node_Browser_Interface_Source.sop
